{
  "stem": "12052.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I, I always was happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was my dream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I came to landing to Los Angeles, and I saw the ocean of endless lights, [LAUGHS] I got scared.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, oh my god, I said, I will get lost in those, between those lights, here with two little kids.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had to sell everything. 12 years of work, and I came with, with minus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had to borrow still money, like $300 from different relatives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And later on, I paid them back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we arrived to Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my aunt and uncle and my cousin were waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we stayed with them, now I don't know, maybe a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we-- I started to work right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I start to earn money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, and we saved up money for the apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, when we-- we had difficultly to find-- we couldn't rent a house, why we didn't have the-- then I didn't have the earnings.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we rented a apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Only, nobody wanted to rent the apartment with two little kids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we told them, the kids are good-mannered kids, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We live a very strict life, very organized life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They would, would rent us, nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Then finally a family, there were just then living just two families in Alhambra.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the family [NON-ENGLISH], they rented us finally a one-bedroom apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the we-- the kids slept in the bedroom, and we sleep in living room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I think so later on we rented the same place, bigger, two-bedroom apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was employed by name Bob Wandries in Alhambra.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I worked with Mercedes Benz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And, of course, I had experience with all the foreign cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- also there was a hard time.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
